trans-unit.source: Describes the versions of the .NET Framework that an application can run on.
trans-unit.target: 描述可以在上執行應用程式的.NET framework 版本。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.CompatibleFramework"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.CompatibleFramework"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Represents the profile of the corresponding .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: 表示對應的.NET Framework 的設定檔。

trans-unit.source: A profile is a subset of the full .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: 設定檔是完整.NET Framework 的子集。

trans-unit.source: For example, the [!INCLUDE[net_client_v35_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v35-long-md.md)] is a subset of the [!INCLUDE[net_v35SP1_long](~/add/includes/net-v35sp1-long-md.md)], and the [!INCLUDE[net_client_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v40-long-md.md)] is a subset of the [!INCLUDE[net_v45](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
For more information, see [.NET Framework Client Profile](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[.NET Framework Client Profile](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> object that represents the profile of the.NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.String>物件，代表.net Framework 的設定檔。</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the supported runtime for the framework.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定架構支援的執行階段。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> object that represents a runtime version of the corresponding .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.String>物件，表示對應的.NET framework 執行階段版本。</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the version of the framework.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定的 framework 版本。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> object that represents the version of a .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.String>物件，代表.NET Framework 版本。</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the XML version for the framework.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定 XML 版本的架構。

trans-unit.source: An array of XML elements that represents the profile of the.NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: 代表.net Framework 的設定檔的 XML 項目陣列。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the XML supported runtime for the framework.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定 XML 支援執行階段架構。

trans-unit.source: An array of XML elements that represents the runtime version of the corresponding .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: XML 元素的陣列，表示對應的.NET Framework 的執行階段版本。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the version of the framework.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定的 framework 版本。

trans-unit.source: An array of XML elements that represents the version of a .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: XML 項目陣列，代表.NET Framework 版本。
